      "duration": 1.39,
      "size": 22176,
      "text": "你有没有看过天气预报中的风向图？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vector-field",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vector-field/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26784,
      "text": "每个位置都有一个箭头，表示那里的风向和风速。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vector-field",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vector-field/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.12,
      "size": 17856,
      "text": "这就是向量场的一个典型例子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vector-field",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-1",
      "filename": "concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vector-field/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "向量场是空间中每一点都对应一个向量的函数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vector-field",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-2",
      "filename": "concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vector-field/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26784,
      "text": "它可以表示速度场、力场、电场等物理量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vector-field",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-3",
      "filename": "concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vector-field/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26640,
      "text": "向量场的可视化通常用箭头或流线来表示。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vector-field",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-4",
      "filename": "concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vector-field/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.65,
      "size": 26352,
      "text": "让我们通过几个例子来理解向量场的特性。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vector-field",
      "section_id": "streamlines",
      "line_id": "stream-1",
      "filename": "streamlines-stream-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vector-field/xiaoxiao/streamlines-stream-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.37,
      "size": 21888,
      "text": "流线是与向量场处处相切的曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vector-field",
      "section_id": "streamlines",
      "line_id": "stream-2",
      "filename": "streamlines-stream-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vector-field/xiaoxiao/streamlines-stream-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "如果向量场表示流体速度，流线就是流体质点的运动轨迹。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vector-field",
      "section_id": "streamlines",
      "line_id": "stream-3",
      "filename": "streamlines-stream-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vector-field/xiaoxiao/streamlines-stream-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "观察屏幕上的流线如何展示向量场的整体结构。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vector-field",
      "section_id": "streamlines",
      "line_id": "stream-4",
      "filename": "streamlines-stream-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vector-field/xiaoxiao/streamlines-stream-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "流线永远不会相交，因为每点只有一个速度方向。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vector-field",
      "section_id": "divergence-curl",
      "line_id": "div-1",
      "filename": "divergence-curl-div-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vector-field/xiaoxiao/divergence-curl-div-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.72,
      "size": 27504,
      "text": "散度衡量向量场在某点的发散或汇聚程度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vector-field",
      "section_id": "divergence-curl",
      "line_id": "div-2",
      "filename": "divergence-curl-div-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vector-field/xiaoxiao/divergence-curl-div-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.25,
      "size": 20016,
      "text": "正散度表示源，负散度表示汇。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vector-field",
      "section_id": "divergence-curl",
      "line_id": "div-3",
      "filename": "divergence-curl-div-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vector-field/xiaoxiao/divergence-curl-div-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.46,
      "size": 23328,
      "text": "旋度衡量向量场在某点的旋转程度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vector-field",
      "section_id": "divergence-curl",
      "line_id": "div-4",
      "filename": "divergence-curl-div-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vector-field/xiaoxiao/divergence-curl-div-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.35,
      "size": 21600,
      "text": "这两个量是分析向量场的核心工具。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vector-field",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-1",
      "filename": "application-app-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vector-field/xiaoxiao/application-app-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.19,
      "size": 19008,
      "text": "向量场在物理学中无处不在。"
